
Pull-request #1425

Solved issue #1393 :  Options for Relative zero position

Features added:
1. Checkbox at `Application Preferences -> Graphic View -> Hide the relative-zero marker`
2. Colorbox at `Application Preferences -> Graphic Colors -> Relative-Zero Marker Color`
3. Enable/disable the `Set relative zero position` and `Lock relative zero position` buttons on showing/hiding the marker

